- I'm aware of that.

488
00:28:42,751 --> 00:28:44,652
I came because
I needed to see you.

489
00:28:45,954 --> 00:28:48,556
I hoped you might
begin to reciprocate.

490
00:28:51,694 --> 00:28:53,595
I'm sorry.

491
00:28:58,867 --> 00:29:01,236
<i>I also came to look
at property.</i>

492
00:29:01,237 --> 00:29:04,839
